6
00:01:19,910 --> 00:01:21,229
If she appears at the door the next moment,

7
00:01:21,229 --> 00:01:22,630
I'd die, no kidding.

8
00:01:22,630 --> 00:01:23,310
Seriously.

9
00:01:23,400 --> 00:01:24,000
You have no idea

10
00:01:24,000 --> 00:01:25,630
that I have not slept well for the past few days.

11
00:01:25,800 --> 00:01:27,360
I have nightmares every night.

12
00:01:28,080 --> 00:01:29,270
It's here, I think.

13
00:01:31,039 --> 00:01:31,870
Zhou Siyue

14
00:01:32,870 --> 00:01:34,190
Song Ziqi, open the door.

15
00:01:35,270 --> 00:01:37,310
Song Ziqi, open the door.

16
00:01:37,590 --> 00:01:39,000
