17
00:01:39,080 --> 00:01:40,720
Don't hide in there and not speak!

18
00:01:41,040 --> 00:01:42,000
Song Ziqi

19
00:01:44,190 --> 00:01:45,110
Open the door.

20
00:01:48,110 --> 00:01:49,360
Shut up.

21
00:01:49,880 --> 00:01:50,720
Song Ziqi

22
00:01:51,520 --> 00:01:53,030
Song Ziqi. Get the heck out.

23
00:01:54,110 --> 00:01:55,550
I know you are here.

24
00:01:56,110 --> 00:01:57,240
Come out now.

25
00:02:03,800 --> 00:02:05,270
You are being suspended, so what?

26
00:02:05,720 --> 00:02:08,000
Do you have to hide here and get so sullen about it?

27
00:02:08,440 --> 00:02:10,520
Get out of the bathroom!

28
00:02:27,600 --> 00:02:28,320
Hello.

29
00:02:29,390 --> 00:02:30,670
You douchebag! You...

30
00:02:32,960 --> 00:02:34,030
There's no need to...

31
00:02:34,030 --> 00:02:34,910
Don't stop me.

32
00:02:34,910 --> 00:02:36,670
Shadi, calm down first.

33
00:02:36,720 --> 00:02:37,670
You two get out.

34
00:02:38,110 --> 00:02:39,470
I want to talk to him alone.

35
00:02:39,880 --> 00:02:40,550
No...

36
00:02:41,670 --> 00:02:42,360
No, you...

37
00:02:57,390 --> 00:02:58,440
How about

38
00:02:59,670 --> 00:03:01,160
I take you back to school?

39
00:03:08,880 --> 00:03:11,440
My bag is still in there.

40
00:03:15,360 --> 00:03:17,240
I'd better wait outside.

41
00:03:23,880 --> 00:03:25,160
Can't you go easy on me?

42
00:03:25,160 --> 00:03:27,270
If you hurt me, I won't be able to become a pilot.

43
00:03:28,670 --> 00:03:30,240
You still want to be a pilot?

44
00:03:30,440 --> 00:03:31,550
Aren't you trying to stay away from everyone?

45
00:03:31,720 --> 00:03:32,829
Aren't you running away?

46
00:03:34,630 --> 00:03:35,630
You didn't pick up your phone.

47
00:03:36,670 --> 00:03:37,800
Your QQ is off-line.

48
00:03:39,160 --> 00:03:40,000
And you just sent me a message,

49
00:03:40,030 --> 00:03:41,600
telling me that I should never try to find you.

50
00:03:42,000 --> 00:03:43,360
Song Ziqi, who do you think you are?

51
00:03:43,520 --> 00:03:45,240
Why did you treat me like that?

52
00:03:45,390 --> 00:03:46,030
I am sorry.

53
00:03:46,190 --> 00:03:47,390
Sorry?

54
00:03:49,080 --> 00:03:50,550
You are just being suspended.

55
00:03:50,600 --> 00:03:51,829
Big deal?

56
00:03:52,040 --> 00:03:53,670
Do you need to avoid me like the plague?

57
00:03:53,760 --> 00:03:55,160
Calm down.

58
00:03:55,160 --> 00:03:56,510
I can't calm down.

59
00:03:57,600 --> 00:03:59,550
Can't you just man up?

60
00:04:01,550 --> 00:04:03,440
You said you wanted to be with me.

61
00:04:05,550 --> 00:04:07,720
You said you wanted to be a pilot.

62
00:04:08,070 --> 00:04:10,320
And it was you who insisted on our long-distance relationship.

63
00:04:11,550 --> 00:04:13,830
And now, something went wrong.

64
00:04:14,230 --> 00:04:16,270
All you want to do is to hide. Not dare to confront it.

65
00:04:16,510 --> 00:04:18,070
Song Ziqi, are you still a man?

66
00:04:18,200 --> 00:04:19,110
Enough!

67
00:04:37,160 --> 00:04:37,880
Ding Xian

68
00:04:38,760 --> 00:04:39,670
Actually...

69
00:04:40,110 --> 00:04:40,920
Sweet potatoes.

70
