71
00:04:49,440 --> 00:04:50,350
Ten yuan for two.

72
00:04:50,880 --> 00:04:51,440
Okay.

73
00:04:56,070 --> 00:04:57,200
I forgot my bag.

74
00:04:57,440 --> 00:04:58,390
You forgot to bring your money?

75
00:05:00,200 --> 00:05:02,160
Young man, your girlfriend doesn't have money with her.

76
00:05:02,350 --> 00:05:03,950
Come and pay!

77
00:05:11,670 --> 00:05:12,600
Song Ziqi

78
00:05:13,510 --> 00:05:14,760
I miss you.

79
00:05:16,600 --> 00:05:18,270
Go back.

80
00:05:18,880 --> 00:05:20,440
